name: sa2_healthriskfactors_modelledestimate
title: SA2 Health Risk Factors - Modelled Estimate 2011-2013

keyword: alcohol, overweight, obese, risk factors, smoking, smokers, health, population
abstract: Modelled estimates of health risk factors: alcohol consumption, weight and smoking by SA2, 2011-13. SA2 data for these indicators are derived from Population Health Area (PHA) data. PHAs are comprised of one or more whole SA2s. A full listing of SA2s and what percentage of their corresponding PHA has been allocated to them can be found at the following link:  http://publichealth.gov.au/AURIN/phidu_PHA_to_SA2_concordance.xls
